==English==

===Etymology===
Condensation of ''falls from the skies'', term coined by [[cryptozoologist]] Ivan T Sanderson.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# [[precipiation|Precipiation]] of objects from the sky that are not normally expected e.g. frogs, fish, coins etc.

